===芝加哥小熊===
2008年7月8日，運動家以哈登和[[查德·高汀|查德·高汀]]和小熊交易Matt Murton、Eric Patterson、Sean Gallagher和一名小聯盟的捕手<ref>{{cite news | title=Cubs acquire right-handed pitchers Rich Harden and Chad Gaudin from Oakland | date=2008-07-08 | publisher=cubs.mlb.com | url=http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20080708&content_id=3091876&vkey=pr_chc&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | work=Associated Press | accessdate=2008-07-26 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119160808/http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20080708&content_id=3091876&vkey=pr_chc&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | archivedate=2017-01-19 }}</ref>。7月12日是哈登成為小熊球員以後的第一場先發，對手為[[舊金山巨人|舊金山巨人]]，主投5.1局0失分，在他退場時球隊還以7：0領先，但牛棚卻搞砸他的勝投，小熊最後是以8：7打敗巨人<ref>{{cite news | title=Harden strikes out 10 in debut, Cubs win in 11 | date=2008-07-12 | publisher=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]] | url=http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280712116 | work=Associated Press | accessdate=2008-07-26 | archive-date=2014-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302012817/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280712116 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。接著第二場面對[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]的先發中，哈登主投7局只失1分，但球隊沒有得到任何分數，最後球隊以0：2輸球，哈登也吞下敗投<ref>{{cite news | first=Bob | last=Baum | coauthors= | title=Arizona’s Johnson beats Cubs again, 2-0 | date=2008-07-22 | publisher=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]] | url=http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280721129 | accessdate=2008-07-26 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203022/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280721129 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first= | last= | coauthors= | title=Florida 3, Chi Cubs 2, 12 innings | date=2008-07-26 | publisher=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]] | url =http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/boxscore;_ylt=AhyhdusdkZ_B0l9S0MiYWM4RvLYF?gid=280726116 | accessdate = 2008-07-26}}</ref>。哈登在小熊獲得的第1勝是在7月31日對[[密爾瓦基釀酒人|密爾瓦基釀酒人]]的比賽<ref>{{cite news | first=Colin | last=Fly | title=Edmonds hits slam, Cubs finish sweep of Brewers | date=2008-07-31 | publisher=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]] | url=http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280731108 | work=Associated Press | accessdate=2008-07-31 | archive-date=2014-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302012856/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=280731108 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。哈登在這3年總計獲得15勝4敗的成績，獲得0.789高的勝率<ref>Chuck, Bill. [http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/100_random_things_2009/ 100 random things about the Red Sox, Rays, and Yankees] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/100_random_things_2009/ |date=20090813021021 }}, ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]''. Published April 2, 2009.</ref>。10月8日，小熊和哈登簽下1年700萬美金的合約<ref name="Ginsburg">{{cite news|first= Steve|last= Ginsburg|coauthors= Pritha Sarkar|title= Cubs pick up the option on right-hander Hardin|url= http://www.reuters.com/article/sportsNews/idUSTRE497BS220081008|publisher= [[Reuters|Reuters]]|date= 2008-10-08|accessdate= 2008-10-09|archive-date= 2021-03-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210309022148/https://www.reuters.com/article/sportsNews/idUSTRE497BS220081008|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

===德州遊騎兵===
2009年12月10日，哈登和[[德州遊騎兵|德州遊騎兵]]簽下1年650萬美金加上2011年球隊選擇權的合約<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091209&content_id=7783458&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Harden inks new deal with Rangers |access-date=2010-02-02 |archive-date=2014-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221221604/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091209&content_id=7783458&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月9日，哈登被遊騎兵釋出。之後再跟老東家運動家簽下1年合約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://oakland.athletics.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20101215&content_id=16324756&vkey=news_oak&c_id=oak|title=Harden returns to A's with one-year deal|author=Jane Lee|publisher=MLB|date=December 22, 2010|accessdate=2015-01-08|language=en|archive-date=2010-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101218172712/http://oakland.athletics.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20101215&content_id=16324756&vkey=news_oak&c_id=oak|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

