哈登投球只用兩種球種，包括[[快速球|快速球]]和[[變速球|變速球]] <ref>{{Citation|last=Verducci |first=Tom |author-link=Tom Verducci |title=Deadlink |newspaper=[[sports_Illustrated|sports Illustrated]] |volume= |issue= |pages=195–202 |year=2006 |date=2006-04-26 |url=http://www.robneyer.com/book_04_extras2.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080801174947/http://www.robneyer.com/book_04_extras2.html |archivedate=2008-08-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite video  | people = [[Chris_Singleton_(baseball)|Chris Singleton]]  | title = [http://videos.espn.com/m/video/20399050/baseball_tonight_minute_july_12_2008.htm Baseball Tonight Minute July 12, 2008]
  | medium = TV  | publisher = ESPN  |date = 2008}}</ref>，他的快速球約在93–95 mph，有時候能夠達到100 mph，在投出快速球以後，會搭配較慢速的變速球來解決打擊者，讓哈登即使只有兩種球路，也能夠順利解決打擊者<ref name='pitch'>{{cite news | first=Mychael | last=Urban | coauthors= | title=Notes: Harden has the full arsenal | date=2005-07-15 | publisher= | url=http://oakland.athletics.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20050715&content_id=1132280&vkey=news_oak&fext=.jsp&c_id=oak | work=mlb.com | pages= | accessdate=2008-07-31 | language= | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304021204/http://oakland.athletics.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20050715&content_id=1132280&vkey=news_oak&fext=.jsp&c_id=oak | archivedate=2012-03-04 }}</ref>。

